OL,6,FA woman has been sentenced to life in
OL,7,Fprison for murdering her husband and
OL,8,Fhiding his body in a bag in their
OL,9,Fgarden in Canterbury.
OL,11,FFormer law student Maureen Rickards
OL,12,Fwasn't present in court on Wednesday
OL,13,Fto be told she will spend a minimum of
OL,14,F22 years behind bars for the brutal
OL,15,Fmurder of 65-year-old Jeremy Rickards.
