OL,6,FThe hearing was briefly delayed as
OL,7,FRickards, who suffers from diabetes,
OL,8,Ftold the court via video link from HMP
OL,9,FBronzefield her blood glucose levels
OL,10,Fwere low as she said she hadn't eaten
OL,11,Flunch and was suffering from a "hypo".
OL,13,FShe told the judge: "Mentally I'm
OL,14,Frefusing the sentencing because
OL,15,Fphysically I'm ill."
OL,17,FThe court allowed her 15 minutes to
OL,18,Fhave some food, with the judge telling
OL,19,Fher she was not "obliged" to attend,
OL,20,Fand Rickards decided not to return.
