OL,6,FMaureen Rickards, 50, had subjected
OL,7,Fher husband to a campaign of abuse in
OL,8,Fthe weeks leading up to his death.
OL,10,FJeremy Rickards, 65, had been reported
OL,11,Fmissing from the North Holmes Road
OL,12,Farea of Canterbury, Kent on 5 July
OL,13,F2024 having not been seen since 7 June.
OL,15,FFollowing efforts to find him, his
OL,16,Fwife was arrested. Forensic teams
OL,17,Fattended the address and three
OL,18,Fproperties were cordoned off.
