OL,6,FRickards messaged her daughter to say
OL,7,Fthat her father had taken his own life
OL,8,Fin Saudi Arabia. The daughter then
OL,9,Freported her father as missing to the
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FWhen officers checked the garden of
OL,13,Fthe property, they detected a smell in
OL,14,Fthe garden and found a bag with the
OL,15,Fremains of Jeremy's body.
OL,17,FA trial at Canterbury Crown Court
OL,18,Fheard that Rickards stabbed her
OL,19,Fhusband five times, and kept his body
OL,20,Fin a cupboard in her room.
