OL,3,CWife sentenced for murdering husband
OL,4,Cand hiding his body in their garden
OL,6,F"She subjected her partner to a
OL,7,Fcampaign of sustained abuse, before
OL,8,Fviciously murdering him. The attacks
OL,9,Fon Jeremy became more severe in the
OL,10,Frun-up to his murder, leaving him
OL,11,Ffrail, battered and bruised, with
OL,12,Feveryone who came into contact with
OL,13,Fhim concerned for his wellbeing.
OL,15,F"Maureen has never taken
OL,16,Fresponsibility for her actions nor
OL,17,Fshown any remorse for murdering
OL,18,FJeremy. He was subjected to an
OL,19,Fappalling attack.
